<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a style="color: #ff6e6e;" href="#r15"><sup>15</sup></a> <span id="f15"> Houghton, Box 2, GWB to WCT, 27 August 1911.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a style="color: #ff6e6e;" href="#r16"><sup>16</sup></a> <span id="f16"> Houghton, Box 1, Script of 7 October 1911, original.</span></span></p>
